Company Chicken & Rice

1 ½ Cups Rice					2 cups water
1 cut- up chicken				¼ cup chopped onion
1 can cream of chicken soup			¼ tsp pepper

Directions
1. Heat the oven to 350 degrees
2. Grease baking dish and pour rice
3. Place chicken on top of rice
4. Mix together soup, water, onion and pepper then pour over chicken. Cover pan tightly
5. Bake at 350 degrees for 1 ½ hours or until rice is done
